14 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-ICC Labs Applies For Regulatory Approval For New 1 Mln Square Foot Greenhouse Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 7 (Reuters) - Icc Labs Inc: 
* ICC LABS ANNOUNCES APPLICATION FOR REGULATORY APPROVAL FOR NEW 1 MILLION SQUARE FOOT GREENHOUSE FOR THE PRODUCTION AND EXPORT OF THC DRY FLOWERS AND ITS DERIVATIVES FOR MEDICINAL PURPOSES 
* ICC LABS INC - ‍ICC LABS EXPECTS TO COMMENCE ASSEMBLY OF NEW GREENHOUSE AS SOON AS IT RECEIVES REGULATORY APPROVAL WHICH IS ANTICIPATED IN MAY 2018​ Source text for Eikon:
